name: Delivery Doggo
description:
You are trapped in the Doggo planet and the only way to return home is by delivering packages!! 

How fast can you finish the game? (It takes less than 5 min to beat) 

D Or -> to drive forward

Spacebar to Jump

Design: Cecilia Cecchet - Instagram

Code and Audio: David Potolski - LinkedIn - YT - Spotify
